Package: pax
Type: Package
Title: A Package Templating Package
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2015-05-02
Author: Tyler Rinker <tyler.rinker@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Tyler Rinker <tyler.rinker@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: curl, rmarkdown
Suggests: testthat, knitr
LazyData: TRUE
Description: A templating system for R packages that assumes the use of
        GitHub, RStudio, 'testthat', Travis-CI and 'covr' (coveralls).
